<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">

<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Your Account Credentials - {{app_name}}</title>
</head>

<body style="margin:0;font-family:arial">
    <table style="border:0;width:100%">
        <tr style="background:#eeeeee">
            <td style="padding:20px;color:#808080;text-align:center;font-size:40px;font-weight:600">
                {{app_name}}
            </td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
            <td style="padding:20px;color:#808080;font-size:16px;font-weight:100">
                <h2 style="color:#333;margin-bottom:20px">Welcome {{userName}}!</h2>
                <p>Your account has been successfully created on {{app_name}}.</p>
                <p>You can now access your account using the credentials below:</p>
                
                <div style="background:#f5f5f5;padding:20px;border-radius:5px;margin:20px 0">
                    <p style="margin:10px 0"><strong>Email:</strong> {{email}}</p>
                    <p style="margin:10px 0"><strong>Temporary Password:</strong> <code style="background:#fff;padding:5px 10px;border-radius:3px;font-size:16px">{{tempPassword}}</code></p>
                </div>
                
                <p style="color:#d32f2f;font-weight:bold;margin-top:20px">⚠️ Important Security Notice:</p>
                <p>For your security, please change your password immediately after your first login.</p>
                
                <p>You can access the portal by clicking the button below:</p>
            </td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
            <td style="text-align:center;padding:20px">
                <a href="{{loginUrl}}"
                    style="display:inline-block;padding:15px 30px;background:#00838f;text-decoration:none;color:#ffffff;border-radius:5px;font-weight:bold">Login to Your Account</a>
            </td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
            <td style="padding:20px;color:#808080;font-size:14px">
                <p><strong>What you can do:</strong></p>
                <ul style="line-height:1.8">
                    <li>View your profile and update your information</li>
                    <li>Access class schedules and assignments</li>
                    <li>View grades and performance reports</li>
                    <li>Communicate with teachers and administrators</li>
                    {{#if isParent}}
                    <li>Monitor your child's academic progress</li>
                    <li>View invoices and make payments</li>
                    {{/if}}
                </ul>
            </td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
            <td style="padding:20px;color:#808080;font-size:14px;text-align:center">
                <p>If you have any questions or need assistance, please don't hesitate to contact our support team.</p>
                <p>Best regards,<br>The {{app_name}} Team</p>
            </td>
        </tr>
    </table>
</body>

</html>

